title: SwifTEA: This Love (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor! What is going on here? Another song from 1989 has been re-released, along with a bunch of merch from two different eras! What does all of this mean? And what do her latest captions suggest? We deep dive into it all!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
